postText: Mmmmm I love creamed corn. It's so gooey and creamy y'all
Have y'all ever had creamed corn? It's so yummy it fills my soul up y'all mmmmm
Cream corn is so low in high fructose corn syrup it is a real superfood. Yum!
Just finised my rough draft of the cream corn manifesto. I hope one day the whole world will know how delicious it is :)
Cream corn is just so fantastic, I just can't get enough!
Yo y'all have to check out this type of corn; it's the most amazing thing!
My cream corn teammates are better than your regular teammates.
